HEADWORD: Hogchoker
<hw>Hog"chok`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An American sole (<spn>Achirus lineatus</spn> syn. <spn>Achirus
achirus</spn>), related to the European sole, but of no market
value.</def>⟦br⟧
